examples.en: He is in charge of recruitment.

examples.en: The Air Force is mounting an aggressive pilot recruitment campaign.

examples.en: She was given absolute control over all recruitment decisions.

examples.en: My task was to prepare the ground for the recruitment of support workers.
examples.ru: Моя задача состояла в том, чтобы подготовить почву для вербовки работников поддержки.
